<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your OTP Code - STEM Mantra</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066FF 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .logo span {
      color: #FFC107;
    }
    .tagline {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .message {
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .otp-container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border: 2px dashed #0066FF;
    }
    .otp-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0066FF;
      letter-spacing: 12px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .expiry {
      color: #dc2626;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .warning-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #92400e;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .warning-text {
      color: #78350f;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #e2e8f0, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .help-text {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .help-text a {
      color: #0066FF;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer-logo span {
      color: #FFC107;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .social-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 8px;
      line-height: 40px;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer-address {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">STEM <span>Mantra</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">Master The Skills ‚Ä¢ Drive Your Future</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="greeting">Hello <%= firstName %>! üëã</h1>
      <p class="message">
        <% if (purpose === 'verification') { %>
          Welcome to STEM Mantra! Please use the following OTP to verify your email address and complete your registration.
        <% } else if (purpose === 'login') { %>
          You've requested to log in to your STEM Mantra account. Use the following OTP to continue.
        <% } else if (purpose === 'reset-password') { %>
          We received a request to reset your password. Use the following OTP to proceed with the password reset.
        <% } else { %>
          Here's your one-time password for verification.
        <% } %>
      </p>
      
      <div class="otp-container">
        <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        <div class="expiry">‚è∞ This code expires in <%= expiryMinutes %> minutes</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <div class="warning-title">üîí Security Notice</div>
        <div class="warning-text">
          Never share this code with anyone. STEM Mantra will never ask you for this code via phone or message.
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="divider"></div>
      
      <p class="help-text">
        Didn't request this code? You can safely ignore this email.<br>
        Need help? <a href="mailto:support@stemmantra.com">Contact our support team</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">STEM <span>Mantra</span></div>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#">üìò</a>
        <a href="#">üê¶</a>
        <a href="#">üì∏</a>
        <a href="#">üíº</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-text">
        ¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> STEM Mantra. All rights reserved.
      </div>
      <div class="footer-address">
        C-104 2nd Floor, Noida Sec-10, UP ‚Äì 201301 | +91-6356631515
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
